OL,3,CTwo-child benefit cap could be
OL,4,Cscrapped in Budget, hints Reeves
OL,6,FRachel Reeves has hinted she could
OL,7,Fscrap the controversial two-child
OL,8,Fbenefit cap in the upcoming Autumn
OL,9,FBudget.
OL,11,FThe chancellor said she does not think
OL,12,Fchildren should be "penalised" for
OL,13,Fbeing part of large families, adding
OL,14,Fthat "we'll take further measures" to
OL,15,Fend child poverty in the Budget later
OL,16,Fthis month.
