OL,3,CTwo-child benefit cap could be
OL,4,Cscrapped in Budget, hints Reeves
OL,6,FITV News understands ministers have
OL,7,Fbeen told the government is planning
OL,8,Fto lift the cap, following increasing
OL,9,Fpressure from within the Labour Party,
OL,10,Fincluding from former prime minister
OL,11,Fand chancellor Gordon Brown.
OL,13,FThe chancellor's latest comments are
OL,14,Fthe clearest public signal she has
OL,15,Fgiven so far that she plans to do so.
OL,17,FReeves was asked how she would justify
OL,18,Fhiking taxes for some while increasing
OL,19,Fbenefits for others, amid speculation
OL,20,Fover the actions she will unveil at
OL,21,Fher November 26 statement.
