OL,3,CTwo-child benefit cap could be
OL,4,Cscrapped in Budget, hints Reeves
OL,6,FShe told BBC 5Live it was important
OL,7,Fnot to let the "costs to our economy
OL,8,Fin allowing child poverty to go
OL,9,Funchecked".
OL,11,FReeves added: "In the end, a child
OL,12,Fshould not be penalised because their
OL,13,Fparents don't have very much money.
OL,15,F"Now, in many cases you might have a
OL,16,Fmum and a dad who were both in work,
OL,17,Fbut perhaps one of them has developed
OL,18,Fa chronic illness, perhaps one of them
OL,19,Fhas passed away.
