OL,3,CTwo-child benefit cap could be
OL,4,Cscrapped in Budget, hints Reeves
OL,6,F"There are plenty of reasons why
OL,7,Fpeople make decisions to have three,
OL,8,Ffour children, but then find
OL,9,Fthemselves in difficult times."
OL,11,FAdoption or foster caring might also
OL,12,Ffactor into things, she said during
OL,13,Fthe interview in No 11 Downing Street.
OL,15,F"Lots and lots of different reasons
OL,16,Fwhy families change shape and size
OL,17,Fover time, and I don't think that it's
OL,18,Fright that a child is penalised
OL,19,Fbecause they are in a bigger family
OL,20,Fthrough no fault of their own.
