OL,3,CTwo-child benefit cap could be
OL,4,Cscrapped in Budget, hints Reeves
OL,6,FThe two-child limit ` first announced
OL,7,Fin 2015 by the Conservatives and which
OL,8,Fcame into effect in 2017 ` restricts
OL,9,Fchild tax credit and universal credit
OL,10,F(UC) to the first two children in most
OL,11,Fhouseholds.
OL,13,FCampaigners from the Child Poverty
OL,14,FAction Group argue that 109 children
OL,15,Facross the UK are pulled into poverty
OL,16,Fby the policy every day.
