OL,6,FThe chancellor's comments came after
OL,7,Fthe former Prime Minister Gordon Brown
OL,8,Fsaid he was "confident" the government
OL,9,Fwould make changes to the limit at the
OL,10,Fupcoming Budget.
OL,12,FBrown told Sky News in an interview
OL,13,Fpublished Monday: "I am confident that
OL,14,Fthe two-child rule will be addressed.
OL,16,F"We're waiting for Rachel Reeves's
OL,17,Fbudget, which I think will mention
OL,18,Fthis.
OL,20,F"Keir Starmer, I know, is personally
OL,21,Fconcerned and interested in this.
